	<h3>Troubleshooting and Support (actually, lack of it)</h3>
	<p>Reporting bugs at http://bugs.debian.org is out of question for these packages. However, you are welcome to help Debian Qt/KDE team to improve packaging by making the patch or proposing/discussing solutions (complaining does not count).</p>
	<p>For more information on the making of the Live CD ping dpalacio on the irc channel.</p>
